Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,さとりさんが化物だとしたら　二人はさながら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔物と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,のの
